  "pageTitle": "请介绍一下您的废弃物回收项目",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"contact-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">联系方式 / 询问</p>\n        <h1 id=\"contact-title\">请介绍一下您的废弃物回收项目</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">如需更有用的建议，请分享您的废弃物类型、目标容量、场地限制、目的地国家以及您考虑的产品方向。这给WEI LAN足够的背景，可以正式开始工程讨论。</p>\n        <div class=\"page-chip-row\" aria-label=\"项目信息亮点\">\n          <span>废弃物类型</span>\n          <span>容量目标</span>\n          <span>场地面积</span>\n          <span>输出目标</span>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"form-title\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">项目咨询</p>\n          <h2 id=\"form-title\">发送你的材料、目标容量和场地限制</h2>\n          <p>收到项目详情后，工程团队可以审查废弃物流、容量目标、现场状况和自动化预期，并推荐合适的系统配置路径。</p>\n          <div class=\"process-list\" aria-label=\"后续流程\">\n            <span>工程评测</span>\n            <span>配置建议</span>\n            <span>技术提案</span>\n            <span>报价讨论</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\" data-contact-form action=\"/api/contact\" method=\"post\">\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            名称\n            <input name=\"name\" autocomplete=\"name\" required>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            邮箱\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" autocomplete=\"email\" required>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            公司\n            <input name=\"company\" autocomplete=\"organization\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field\">\n            WhatsApp / 电话\n            <input name=\"phone\" autocomplete=\"tel\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            国家/地区\n            <input name=\"country\" autocomplete=\"country-name\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            目标容量\n            <input name=\"capacity\" placeholder=\"例如：2 t/h或100 t/h\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-narrow\">\n            可用 站点区域\n            <input name=\"siteArea\" placeholder=\"工厂占地面积或布局限制\">\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-full\">\n            产品兴趣\n            <span class=\"product-interest-picker\" data-product-picker>\n              <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"product\" data-product-value required>\n              <button class=\"product-interest-control\" type=\"button\" data-product-control aria-haspopup=\"listbox\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n                <span data-product-label>选择产品线</span>\n                <span class=\"product-interest-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </button>\n              <span class=\"product-interest-menu\" data-product-menu role=\"listbox\" aria-label=\"产品兴趣\">\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"AI optical sorting center\" role=\"option\">AI光学分拣中心</button>\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"Construction and bulky waste recycling line\" role=\"option\">建筑与大型废物回收线</button>\n                <button class=\"product-interest-option\" type=\"button\" data-product-option=\"Both systems\" role=\"option\">两种系统</button>\n              </span>\n            </span>\n          </label>\n          <div class=\"form-field form-field-full waste-type-field\" data-waste-type-field>\n            <span class=\"field-label\" id=\"waste-type-label\">废弃物类型</span>\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wasteType\" data-waste-type-value>\n            <div class=\"waste-type-picker\" data-waste-picker>\n              <button class=\"waste-type-control is-placeholder\" type=\"button\" data-waste-control aria-labelledby=\"waste-type-label\" aria-haspopup=\"listbox\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-disabled=\"true\" disabled>\n                <span data-waste-label>先选择产品线</span>\n                <span class=\"waste-type-chevron\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              </button>\n              <div class=\"waste-type-menu\" data-waste-menu>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-options\" data-waste-options role=\"listbox\" aria-label=\"废物类型建议\"></div>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-create-row\">\n                  <input data-waste-custom autocomplete=\"off\" placeholder=\"类型 自定义废弃物类型\">\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-custom-clear\" type=\"button\" data-waste-custom-clear aria-label=\"清除自定义废弃物类型\">×</button>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"waste-type-menu-actions\">\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-clear\" type=\"button\" data-waste-clear>全部</button>\n                  <button class=\"waste-type-done\" type=\"button\" data-waste-done>完成</button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <label class=\"form-field form-field-full\">\n            详情项目\n            <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"材料成分、输出目标、电压、自动化需求、时间线\" required></textarea>\n          </label>\n          <div class=\"form-submit-row\">\n            <p class=\"contact-note\">销售热线：+86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p>\n            <button type=\"submit\">工程提案请求</button>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"form-status\" data-contact-status role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\"></p>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section service-section\" aria-labelledby=\"next-steps-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">后续流程</p>\n          <h2 id=\"next-steps-title\">从询问到提案讨论的简单路径</h2>\n          <p>大多数项目一开始不需要漫长的发现阶段。明确的首次RFQ通常足以进入实际技术审查。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-grid\">\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">01</span>\n            <h3>提交项目 详情</h3>\n            <p>发送废料类型、目标容量和厂房限制，以便团队了解运营背景。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">02</span>\n            <h3>工程评测</h3>\n            <p>WEI LAN会先审查物料类型、可能的工艺模块以及整体项目方向，然后再讨论配置。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">03</span>\n            <h3>系统推荐</h3>\n            <p>团队推荐最合适的产品线、工艺路径和配置范围，以便进行更深入的评估。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"service-card\">\n            <span class=\"number\">04</span>\n            <h3>提案与报价讨论</h3>\n            <p>一旦基本契合度明确，讨论可以进入文档、参数和商业讨论。</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section\" aria-labelledby=\"checklist-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">调查清单</p>\n          <h2 id=\"checklist-title\">提升提案质量最快的四个输入</h2>\n          <p>即使是简短的第一条信息，只要包含以下操作基础，也会更加可操作。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-grid\">\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">输入01</span>\n            <h3>废物类型与成分</h3>\n            <p>明确材料是PET、HDPE、PP、混合塑料、C&D 废弃物、装饰废料还是大块废弃物。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">输入02</span>\n            <h3>目标容量</h3>\n            <p>分享预期的小时吞吐量，以便推荐能保持在合适的型号和模块范围内。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">输入03</span>\n            <h3>场地条件</h3>\n            <p>可用可移动的占地面积、布局限制、电压和局部工作限制都会影响解的方向。</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-card\">\n            <span class=\"resource-type\">输入04</span>\n            <h3>预期产出</h3>\n            <p>说明你希望系统使用回收产品、纯度目标或最终材料方向，比如说支持。</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"cta-band\" aria-labelledby=\"rfq-support-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">需要更多背景信息吗？</p>\n        <h2 id=\"rfq-support-title\">您也可以在提交表格前查看产品、解决方案和资源</h2>\n        <p>如果团队仍在比较选项，可以使用配套页面缩小项目方向，然后返回最相关的废弃物流和容量目标。</p>\n        <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/products\">探索产品线</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">评测资源</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
